                Improvements to Clear Lake
              </h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
                Members make major improvements to Clear Lake property, including septic tank, parking area, and leach field.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-[calc(25%+0.0625rem)] lg:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-blue-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg z-10">
          </div>
        </div>

        <%!-- 1967 - Clear Lake bathroom construction --%>
        <div
          data-timeline-item
          data-tags="cabin life"
          class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-start gap-8 group"
        >
